{"id":232941917,"title":"第一次做蒔蘿馬鈴薯濃湯就上手","content":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRs.jpg\n(๑•̀ᄇ•́)و\n材料：\n小洋蔥一顆\n奶油\n小把蒔蘿\n馬鈴薯一顆\n中筋麵粉\n1.鍋中加入大塊奶油以最小火熱鍋，稍微溶化後加入洋蔥末拌炒至變軟變色。\n2.加入麵粉拌炒(分次加入)，炒至成麵糰狀後，加入高湯(清水也可)，轉中火，將麵糰煮開並將鍋底精華刮起。\n3.倒入切好的滾刀狀馬鈴薯，以及切成小段狀的蒔蘿莖部並煮至湯滾。\n4.調味，加入鹽及新鮮黑胡椒，然後加入乳酪絲或鮮奶油或牛奶。\n5.起鍋前先用筷子刺進馬鈴薯確認熟透，裝碗，擺放些許蒔蘿葉裝飾。\n然後美味的濃湯就完成啦(*ﾟ∀ﾟ)","excerpt":"（๑•̀ᄇ•́）و，材料：小洋蔥一顆，奶油，小把蒔蘿，馬鈴薯一顆，中筋麵粉，1.鍋中加入大塊奶油以最小火熱鍋，稍微溶化後加入洋蔥末拌炒至變軟變色。2.加入麵粉拌炒（分次加入），炒至成麵糰狀後，加入高湯","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":23,"tags":[],"topics":["濃湯","食譜","馬鈴薯","蒔蘿","烹飪"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"國立屏東大學","department":"財務金融學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":23}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRs.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"aa69d4f1-17c9-43f1-8ec6-359db6b49119","url":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRsl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRsl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRsl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z"},{"id":"aa69d4f1-17c9-43f1-8ec6-359db6b49119","url":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRs.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/9rYuHRs","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9rYuHRsl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-23T02:10:25.008Z"}],"postAvatar":""}